Description: Thank you for visiting our ebay store! Live life easier with reisenthel! Thanks to its doctor's bag design, the allrounder L bag by reisenthel is a really roomy travel bag that can circumvent the world effortlessly with its contents neatly stowed inside. Whether for a quick overnight trip, or an extended getaway, this bag is the perfect accessory for travel and fits carry-on luggage requirements on nearly every airline. A classic design in a classic, solid black, mix and match this bag with other reisenthel products to complete all of your travel and toting needs. The reisenthel allrounder L bag bag is made from easy-to-clean, premium quality, water-repellent polyester and measures 19-inches long by 11-1/2-inches wide by 15-1/2-inches high. With a rounded satchel look, this bag opens up wide and features a generous main compartment with 6 smaller interior pockets for ultimate organization and protection. Featuring padded carrying handles, removable, adjustable shoulder straps with supports, padded base and sides, this bag offers an extra layer of protection for the frequent traveler. Since 1971, reisenthel has been synonymous with innovative ideas, functional design and delightful everyday helpers. They aim for simplicity making each product straightforward and uncomplicated. Innovative, intelligent and practical - these are qualities that make reisenthel products what they are. - Great for everyday use in all types of travel; contemporary design modeled after the traditional doctor's bag for ultimate mobility and organization - 6 inside pockets for practical storage; lightly padded base and sides; water-repellent; features a classic, solid black - Zip fastening with integrated metal bracket; 2 carrying handles with grip; carrying strap with comfortably padded shoulder supports - Premium quality polyester; measures 19-inches long by 11-1/2-inches wide by 15-1/2-inches high; strap drop measures 6-1/4-inches; Black - For maintenance, wipe with a damp cloth only; Imported reisenthel Allrounder L, Weekender Bag, Black
